Cmd=-threads {threads} {offset} {realtime} -i "{infile}" -threads {threads} -f mpegts -vcodec libx264 -bufsize 1024k -b:v 1200k -bt 1300k {framerate} -map 0:0 -map 0:1 -vf "yadif, scale={scalex}:{scaley}" -preset {vpreset} -tune film -vprofile baseline -level 30 -acodec libmp3lame -ab 192k -ar 44100 -ac 2 -async 1 -y "{outfile}"
maxWidth=800
maxHeight=640
MimeType=video/mpeg
Ext=.ts

[WP 768 kbit]
Cmd=-threads {threads} {offset} {realtime} -i "{infile}" -threads {threads} -f mpegts -vcodec libx264 -bufsize 1024k -b:v 470k -bt 520k {framerate} -map 0:0 -map 0:1 -vf "yadif, scale={scalex}:{scaley}" -preset {vpreset} -tune film -vprofile baseline -level 30 -acodec libmp3lame -ab 96k -ar 44100 -ac 2 -async 1 -y "{outfile}"
maxWidth=704
maxHeight=496
MimeType=video/mpeg
Ext=.ts

[WP audio 128 kbit]
Cmd=-threads {threads} {offset} {realtime} -i "{infile}" -f mpegts -vn -acodec libmp3lame -ab 128k -ar 44100 -ac 2 -y -threads {threads} "{outfile}"
MimeType=audio/mpeg
ext=.ts
